      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This unit features eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission offers crisp gear transitions, paired with a variable M differential lock to optimize torque distribution across the rear axle. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including addressed rod bearings and throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functionality, ensuring precise damping characteristic adjustments. It sits on staggered alloy wheels with consistent tread depth, showing only minor cosmetic wear commensurate with its age. A driver-focused example with excellent structural integrity and a clean underbody.",
